    <h2>SWSDI Privacy Policy</h2>
    <hr />
    <p>We at SWSDI are thoroughly committed to your privacy. It's very important to us.</p>
    <p>Therefore, any information we collect, we collect strictly for the purpose of our own records.</p>
    <p>We will only pass on the minimum information required to our partners, to enable them to provide us with the services necessary to have a successful camp.</p>
    <p>Digital input collected through Facebook OAuth is strictly for our own records. We won't put silly things on your facebook wall without your explicit permission to do so. We will use the information gathered strictly for the purpose of managing our camp application process.</p>
    <p>The health and insurance information you provide is kept in the strictest confidence, and only provided to ASU Campus Health Services, or a local hospital, if it is necessary for the treatment of illness or injury.</p>
    <p>For further information regarding our privacy policy and acknowledgements, please see the <a href="https://register.swsdi.org/documents/returnpacket2015.pdf">Return packet.</a></p>
